metadata.name: Chii's Japanese leek (ちぃず長ネギ)
metadata.description:
Chii's Japanese leek.His favourite place is in his mum's eco-bag, where he likes to just stick his face out and get some wind.
ちぃず長ネギ。好きな場所はお母さんのエコバッグの中で顔だけ出して風を浴びるのが好きみたい。
